name: Pada Nasib, pada Arus
description:
A collaboration piece between singer/songwriter Ananda Badudu, visual artist Gata Mahardika, and music producer/modular enthusiast Indra Perkasa.

The audio in this piece is taken from the original song Pada Nasib, pada Arus written and produced by Ananda Badudu and Indra Perkasa.

The artwork was hand drawn using water color by Gata Mahardika, and then animated by Indra Perkasa
